---
title: Gravy-Smothered Meatballs over Thyme Mashed Potatoes with Roasted Green Beans
description: If gravy is your favorite part of a holiday dinner, we’re with you. That’s why our chefs dreamed up this gravy-licious meal! The beefy meatballs stand proud under the saucy stuff—they’re juicy, delicious, and a perfect complement to tender roasted green beans and thyme-flecked mashed potatoes on the side. Get on the gravy train!
